(251, 'fear', '2010', 18, 0, 6371, 438, 389, 35.96, 'Experience the original F.E.A.R. along with F.E.A.R. Extraction Point and F.E.A.R. Perseus Mandate. Available Now!', '{\'minimum\': \'<strong>Minimum:</strong><br>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Operating System:</strong> Windows® XP, x64 or 2000 with latest service pack installed<br>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Pentium® 4 1.7 GHz or equivalent processor<br>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 512 MB of RAM or more<br>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> 64 MB GeForce™ 4 Ti or Radeon® 9000 video card; Monitor that can display in 4:3 aspect ratio<br>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</li><li><strong>DirectX®:</strong> 9.0c (August Edition) or higher<br>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</li><li><strong>Hard Drive:</strong> 17 GB free Hard Drive Space for installation; Additional hard drive space for a swap file and saved game files<br>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</li><li><strong>Sound:</strong> 16-bit DirectX® 9.0 compliant sound card with support for EAX™ 2.0<br>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</li><li><strong>Multiplayer Requirements:</strong> Broadband or LAN connection for multiplayer games<br>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</li></ul>\', \'recommended\': \'<strong>Recommended:</strong><br>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Pentium® 4 3.0 GHz or equivalent processor<br>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 1 GB RAM<br>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> A 256 MB Radeon® 9800 Pro or GeForce™ 6600 or equivalent supported<br>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</li><li><strong>DirectX®:</strong> DirectX® 9 compliant video card with hardware T&amp;L and pixel shader 2.0 support<br>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</li><li><strong>Sound:</strong> Sound Blaster® X-Fi™ series sound card<br>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t